,\\dots,n\\}$ for which there exists\nan $r$-colouring which contains no monochromatic solutions to $Ax=0$.\n  Along the way a number of open problems are posed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Jan 2017 16:44:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Jul 2017 16:39:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 25 Jun 2018 13:46:21 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 27 Nov 2018 22:19:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-29"}
