tope method and two extremal set system problems that are of independent\ninterest: we maximize the number of $r$-tuples $A_1,A_2,\\dots, A_r \\in {\\cal\nA}$ over all antichains ${\\cal A}\\subseteq 2^{[n]}$ such that (i)\n$\\cap_{i=1}^rA_i=\\emptyset$, (ii) $\\cap_{i=1}^rA_i=\\emptyset$ and\n$\\cup_{i=1}^rA_i=[n]$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Jan 2017 12:21:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Aug 2017 20:23:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-09"}
